# New ports collection makefile for:	xmpeg3
# Version required:	1.0
# Date created:		7 July 1997
# Whom:			doconnor@ist.flinders.edu.au
#
# $Id: Makefile,v 1.4 1998/02/21 22:38:11 fenner Exp $
